2004-08-24 08:17:33 GMT	J. David Ibanez <jdavid@itaapy.com>	patch-67

    Summary:
      catalog, fix search, add the missing class Document
    Revision:
      itools--main--0.4--patch-67

    Every time there is a hit an instance of the Document class is created
    and populated with the stored indexes.
    
    Before, the Document class was missing, but there was another class
    with the same name (used for other purposes), which was used instead
    by mistake.
    
    Changes:
    
      - Rename Document.Document to IDocument.IDocument
      - Add Catalog.Document

    modified files:
     Changelog catalog/Catalog.py catalog/IDocument.py

    renamed files:
     catalog/.arch-ids/Document.py.id
       ==> catalog/.arch-ids/IDocument.py.id
     catalog/Document.py
       ==> catalog/IDocument.py


