    Summary:
      don't cache virtual handlers (handlers.Folder)
    Revision:
      itools--main--0.4--patch-48

    Now virtual handlers are not cached.
    
    Caching them was the cause of a bug within ikaaro, where, once a virtual
    handler was cached, it didn't change with the language selection as it
    should.

