2004-06-02 15:36:52 GMT	J. David Ibanez <jdavid@itaapy.com>	patch-3

    Summary:
      register xml handlers on the xml package
    Revision:
      itools--main--0.4--patch-3

    Until now the xml handlers were registered in the constructor of the
    class handlers.Database (see __init__.py); now they are registered in
    the init file of the xml package.
    
    This avoids a circular import. But it changes the behaviour of the Database
    class and sub-classes (i.e., it could break third party code).

    modified files:
     handlers/Folder.py handlers/__init__.py xml/__init__.py


